dataIdInfo.idAbs: This point data layer represents addresses for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Fond_du_Lac_Addresses_2017.gdb. [The fire address layer depicts fire address locations in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin. Last published: May 21, 2015.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[This data was created to cartographically inform citizens as well as public and private officials of the location of fire addresses in Fond du Lac County.]
